---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';

const pageTitle = "Refund Policy | Jagsy Joy";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Read the Jagsy Joy refund and return policy." />
  </head>

  <body>
    <AnnouncementBar />
    <Header />

    <main>
      <header class="policy-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">POLICY</p>
        <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="container">
        <article class="policy-card">
          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">↩️</span>
              <h2>Return Policy</h2>
            </div>
            <p>We have a 30-day return policy, which means you have 30 days after receiving your item to request a return.</p>
            <p>To be eligible for a return, your item must be in the same condition that you received it, unworn or unused, with tags, and in its original packaging. You’ll also need the receipt or proof of purchase.</p>
            <p>To start a return, you can contact us at <strong>support@finessynyc.com</strong>. If your return is accepted, we’ll send you a return shipping label, as well as instructions on how and where to send your package. Items sent back to us without first requesting a return will not be accepted.</p>
            <p>You can always contact us for any return question at <strong>support@finessynyc.com</strong>.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">⚠️</span>
              <h2>Damages and issues</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Please inspect your order upon reception and contact us immediately if the item is defective, damaged, or if you receive the wrong item, so that we can evaluate the issue and make it right.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">🚫</span>
              <h2>Exceptions / non-returnable items</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Certain types of items cannot be returned, like perishable goods such as food, flowers, or plants, custom products such as special orders or personalized items, and personal care goods such as beauty products. We also do not accept returns for hazardous materials, flammable liquids, or gases. Please get in touch if you have questions or concerns about your specific item.</p>
            <p>Unfortunately, we cannot accept returns on sale items or gift cards.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">🔄</span>
              <h2>Exchanges</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Items can be exchanged within the return policy time frame. Please contact us at <strong>support@finessynyc.com</strong> with your exchange request.</p>
            <p>To be eligible for an exchange, your item must be in the same condition that you received it, unworn or unused, with tags, and in its original packaging. You’ll also need the receipt or proof of purchase.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">💳</span>
              <h2>Refunds</h2>
            </div>
            <p>We will notify you once we’ve received and inspected your return, and let you know if the refund was approved or not. If approved, you’ll be automatically refunded on your original payment method. Please remember it can take some time for your bank or credit card company to process and post the refund too.</p>
          </section>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: #17204A;
    background: #EAFBFF;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.08), transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 90% 4%, rgba(24, 214, 201, 0.08), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #EAFBFF 0%, #F4FDFF 50%, #EEE8FF 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .policy-header {
    padding: 220px 8% 60px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: #17204A;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #17204A;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 8% 120px;
  }

  .policy-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #D1EFFF;
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 60px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.04);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .icon-badge {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #EAFBFF;
    border: 1px solid #D1EFFF;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #17204A;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #5f526b;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  strong {
    color: #17204A;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .policy-header {
      padding-top: 150px;
    }
    
    .policy-card {
      padding: 40px 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>